moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/08/26/19/4F6BE6AC00000578-6100355-image-m-90_1535309929232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F19%2F4F6BE6AC00000578-6100355-image-m-90_1535309929232.jpg&h=aae973c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Horrifying livestream audio from the Madden NFL online gaming tournament captured the screams of players as the gunfire erupted at the Jacksonville Landing in Florida on Sunday afternoon<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/08/26/19/4F6BFC1F00000578-6100355-image-m-78_1535309245670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F19%2F4F6BFC1F00000578-6100355-image-m-78_1535309245670.jpg&h=78c7acb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/08/26/20/4F6BEE9E00000578-6100355-image-m-97_1535311364597.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F20%2F4F6BEE9E00000578-6100355-image-m-97_1535311364597.jpg&h=0b504c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/08/26/20/4F6C169C00000578-6100355-image-m-98_1535311374887.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F20%2F4F6C169C00000578-6100355-image-m-98_1535311374887.jpg&h=02d826c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/08/26/19/4F6BE56E00000578-6100355-image-a-75_1535309066404.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F19%2F4F6BE56E00000578-6100355-image-a-75_1535309066404.jpg&h=ce804e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A livestream from the gaming tournament captured the moment the gunfire broke 